  "title": "And A Body Hits The Floor",
  "summary": "In the opulent botanical atrium of the luxury liner Celestine, Johanna grinds through a humiliating negotiation with the aristocratic Lady Ailah Vieres, seeking introductions to her powerful partners while choking back her contempt. The fugitive warlord Darth Malus, carrying a million-credit bounty Johanna herself posted, glides provocatively through the crowd, taunting the Biscuit Baron executives Veruca Violet, Atsvara, and Euphoria before inserting himself behind Johanna to needle Ailah on her behalf. As Ailah lands a cutting jab about Johanna's dependence on her brother the Imperator, a body crashes through the stained-glass canopy and strikes the gaming floor, shattering the evening's polished theatre. Panic and a ship-wide security lockdown follow; Malus watches with detached fascination while the Sith-raised girls react with chilling calm, and Veruca cannily appoints herself security chief over the Xi Charrian CEO ak as cover to reach safety.",
